Best Seller | The 1802cc German Cruiser. 

This 32cm beast is built from 500+ precision-engineered pieces, bringing heavyweight motorcycle style and function to your hands in 1:8 scale.

Inspired by iconic German engineering, the 1802cc Cruiser features functioning steering, shock-absorbing suspension, and a detailed exposed drivetrain—all wrapped in a low-slung frame that screams road presence.

From its rubber tyres and ventilated brake discs to its mirrors, mud guards, and rear exhaust, every detail fuels the ride. Build it. Admire it. Rule the road—piece by piece.
